SettingsTrait, Receiver, Transmitter, Named, NamedObject, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver, Iterable<Object>
public class SettingsPackage extends Settings
A set of configuration objects stored in a package. The package contains a set of .properties files that are used to instantiate and populate the configuration objects.

See the superclass Settings for details on how this works.

Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
